data.description: Don't miss out on this wonderful home In Stonebrook Subdivision!  SEB school district and just minutes to I-16 for all the commuters.  Upon entering the foyer, is a formal dining room, open floorplan into the living room and kitchen.  Vaulted ceiling in the living room and Beautiful new laminate wood flooring in the living room. Stainless appliances in the kitchen and a nice pantry closet.  Master Bedroom has trey ceilings along with the master bath having double vanities, a separate soaking tub, and stand up shower. Entering into the backyard, is a fully fenced yard for pets, a dog house, and chicken coup.  Both of which can stay or go. Don't miss this one! Call today while rates are low!
